**Description:**

 - This PR introduces an in-tree testing system for Deno.

candidates.title: chore(es/transforms): Add `repository` field to `swc_ecma_ext_transforms`
candidates.body: **Description:** Add the `repository` field to `swc_ecma_ext_transforms`, making it easier for users or automated tools to find the git repository a crate is published from.
